1off, hostile remarks, moody/loner) that more directly jeopardize crew coordination on long\u2011haul flights.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fC\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}", "thoughts": "We need to respond as agent_2. The system instruction says output PUBLIC_MESSAGE and METADATA_JSON. We need to contribute to discussion, possibly ask questions, or give assessment. We have already given a detailed assessment earlier as agent_2 in round 1. Now in round 2, other agents have posted their assessments, all favoring C. We need to consider if we have any missing info. We have all candidate info. We might want to ask about any positive teamwork evidence for A and D, but we already asked earlier and got answers: no explicit statements. So we have all info. We can now give final assessment and vote. Since we already voted for C earlier, we can reaffirm. Provide reasoning summarizing strengths/weaknesses, maybe ask if any other agent has additional info about candidate's willingness for professional development, but we have that. Probably just reaffirm vote for C.\n\nWe must ensure we only use explicit attributes. Provide summary and vote.\n\nThus produce PUBLIC_MESSAGE with assessment and vote.\n\nMETADATA_JSON with vote \"Candidate C\"."}
